title: Crude Birth and Death Rates (per 1,000), England and Wales 1541-2015 - Wrigley and Schofield, Mitchell, UK ONS
description: *Note: Our World In Data compiled the data from the above sources as follows: for the years 1541-1861: Wrigley and Schofield (1981); for the years 1862-2003: Brian Mitchell (2010); for the years 2004-2015: UK Office for National Statistics (2016).
